    {
      "id": "l6-places",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Common places",
      "body": "# Places\n\nPlaces you often need to find:\n\n| English | Hindi |\n|---|---|\n| Station | स्टेशन |\n| Market | बाज़ार |\n| Hospital | अस्पताल |\n| School | स्कूल |\n\nTo ask where a place is, use **Where is the ...?** : *Where is the station?* (स्टेशन कहाँ है?). The question word **Where** comes first, then **is**, then **the** + the place."
    },
    {
